              \r\n                    <div class=\"regular\">\r\n                        <h2><a href=\"http://www.kylemaxwell.com/post/566177/rails-config-rb\">rails_config.rb</a></h2>\r\n                        <pre><code class=\"ruby\">#!/usr/bin/env ruby \nrequire \"open3\"\n`mkdir vendor/gems` unless File.exists? \"vendor/gems\"\ndef v(s, u); piston(\"vendor/plugins/#{s}\",u); end\ndef p(s, u); piston(\"vendor/plugins/#{s}\",u); end\ndef g(*args); args.each{|s| gem(s.to_s) }; end\ndef piston(p, u); cmd(\"piston import #{u} #{p}\"); end\ndef gem(s); cmd(\"cd vendor/gems &amp;&amp; gem unpack #{s}\"); end\ndef cmd(s)\n  Open3.popen3(s) do |stdin, stdout, stderr|\n    $stdout &lt;&lt; stdout.read\n    $stderr &lt;&lt; stderr.read\n  end\nend\n\n# Installs below\nv :rails,             \"http://svn.rubyonrails.org/rails/branches/1-2-stable/\"\np :action_mailer,     \"http://svn.kylemaxwell.com/rails_plugins/action_mailer_optional_tls/trunk/\"\np :annotate_models,   \"http://svn.pragprog.com/Public/plugins/annotate_models/\"\np :restful_authentication, \"http://svn.techno-weenie.net/projects/plugins/restful_authentication/\"\ng :dr_nic_magic_models</code></pre>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n            \r\n                <div class=\"date\">\r\n                    Apr 02\r\n                </div>\r\n            \r\n        \r\n            <div class=\"post\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.kylemaxwell.com/post/532700/htpasswd-on-rails\"><img src=\"/themes/4/link.gif\" \r\n                class=\"permalink\" alt=\"Permalink\"/></a>\r\n\r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                    <div class=\"link\">\r\n                        &#187; <a href=\"http://wota.jp/svn/rails/plugins/branches/stable/htpasswd/README\">htpasswd on Rails</a>\r\n                        \r\n                    </div>\r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n            \r\n                <div class=\"date\">\r\n                    Mar 31\r\n                </div>\r\n            \r\n        \r\n            <div class=\"post\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.kylemaxwell.com/post/475941/this-is-a-universal-law-of-vivisystems\"><img src=\"/themes/4/link.gif\" \r\n                class=\"permalink\" alt=\"Permalink\"/></a>\r\n\r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                    <div class=\"quote\">\r\n                        <span class=\"quote\">\r\n                            <big class=\"quote\"><a href=\"http://www.kylemaxwell.com/post/475941/this-is-a-universal-law-of-vivisystems\">&#147;</a></big> This is a universal law of vivisystems: higher-level complexities cannot be inferred by lower-level existences. Nothing &#8212; no computer or mind, no means of mathematics, physics, or philosophy &#8212; can unravel the emergent pattern dissolved in the parts without actually playing it out. Only playing out a hive will tell you if a colony is immixed in a bee. The theorists put it this way: running a system is the quickest, shortest, and only sure method to discern emergent structures latent in it. There are no shortcuts to actually &#8220;expressing&#8221; a convoluted, nonlinear equation to discover what it does. Too much of its behavior is packed away.\r\n                        </span>\r\n                        <div class=\"source\">&mdash; <a href=\"http://www.kk.org/outofcontrol/ch2-c.html\">Kevin Kelly</a></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\